

Tip12: Combine and Conquer(双剑合璧，天下无敌)

Operator + Motion = Action

Trigger          Effect
c                Change.
d                Delete.
y                Yank into register.
g~               Swap case
gu               Make lowercase
gU               Make uppercase
>                shift right
<                shift left
=                自动缩进
!                Filter {motion} lines through an external program

举例：
dap : 删除整个段落
guaw : 整个单词小写
